# Proprietary/extracted binaries and personal RE working notes — never commit
# (see CLAUDE.md "Nooit committen"): the .so, pulled APKs, and raw Ghidra
# decompile dumps of Ninja's proprietary code all live under tools/artifacts/.
tools/artifacts/
tools/lib/*.so
REBOOT.md
ninja_idtoken.txt

# GATT-send fixtures contain live key material / device identifiers — never
# commit them; only the format-contract README is tracked.
tools/gatt_send/fixtures/*.json
!tools/gatt_send/fixtures/README.md
